First Leg [Jun 15, Centenario Stadium, Montevideo, att: 60.000, ref: Carlos Amarilla   [PAR]]
Peñarol (URU) 0-0 Santos (BRA)
Peñarol: Sebastián Sosa; Alejandro González, Carlos Valdez, 
  Guillermo Rodríguez, Darío Rodríguez; Matías Corujo (Antonio Pacheco 67),
  Luis Aguiar, Nicolás Freitas, Matias Mier (Fabian Estoyanoff 55);
  Alejandro Martinuccio, Juan Manuel Olivera (Diego Alonso 82).
  Coach: Diego Aguirre.
Santos: Rafael; Pará, Bruno Rodrigo, Durval, Alex Sandro; Adriano, Danilo,
  Arouca, Elano (Alan Patrick 78); Neymar, Zé Eduardo (Bruno Aguiar 89).
  Coach: Muricy Ramalho
Yellow Cards: Martinuccio, Corujo, Gonzalez (P); Neymar, Arouca (S)
 
Second Leg [Jun 22, Pacaembu stadium, Sao Paulo, att: 40.000, ref: Sergio Pezzotta (ARG)]
Santos (BRA) 2-1 Peñarol (URU)
  [Neymar 46, Danilo 68; Durval 79og]
Santos: Rafael; Danilo, Edu Dracena, Durval, Leo (Alex Sandro 67);
  Adriano, Arouca, Elano, Paulo Henrique Ganso (Para 86); Neymar,
  Zé Eduardo. Coach: Muricy Ramalho.
Peñarol: Sebastián Sosa; Alejandro González (Emiliano Albín 3
  (Fabián Estoyanoff 78)), Carlos Valdez, Guillermo Rodríguez,
  Darío Rodríguez; Matías Corujo, Luis Aguiar, Nicolás Freitas,
  Matías Mier (Jonathan Urretaviscaya 62); Alejandro Martinuccio,
  Juan Manuel Olivera. Coach: Diego Aguirre.
Yellow Cards: Neymar, Zé Eduardo (S); González, Corujo, Freitas (P)
 
Santos champions.
 
